snippet: Hyo-Joo Kim came from a shot back on the last hole to beat Karrie Webb of Australia by one shot and capture the title, becoming the third youngest major winner at 19 years 2 months.
abstract: Hyo-Joo Kim of South Korea wins golf's Evian Championship, becoming third youngest to win an LPGA major.
lead_paragraph: Hyo-Joo Kim came from a shot back on the last hole to beat Karrie Webb of Australia by one shot and capture the title, becoming the third youngest major winner at 19 years 2 months.

headline.main: South Korean Teenager Edges Karrie Webb to Win at Evian Championship
headline.print_headline: South Korean Teenager Edges Webb to Capture Evian Title
